Program: Outlook
Title: The Plight of Refugees
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p03kbrs3
Last Broadcast Date: Not available
The difficult life of a refugee, story of a Rwandan who fled to Kenya and has to rely on the charity of school friends. Also, Susan Casey and her close encounters with Great White Sharks on the Farallon Islands; Journalists talk about their coverage of conflict in Lebanon, Israel and Iran.